INSERT INTO "torder"(ordid,orddt,custid,empid,create_at,update_at) SELECT q1.ordid, q2.orddt, a3.custid, a4.empid, a5.create_at, a5.update_at FROM "torder" q1 LEFT OUTER JOIN "torder" q2 ON (q2.ordid = q1.ordid)RIGHT OUTER JOIN "torder" a3 ON (a3.ordid IN (q1.ordid, q1.ordid))FULL OUTER JOIN "torder" a4 ON (a4.ordid = q1.ordid)CROSS JOIN "torder" a5 ON (a5.ordid = q1.ordid)
